      "text": "21\nFİZİK BİLİMİ VE KARİYER KEŞFİ\nc) Fizik biliminin hayvanlardaki özelliklerden ilham alarak yaptığı çalışmalara üç örnek veriniz. \n       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �              �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �              �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �              �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �              �       �       �      