lmesi gereken yönlerinizle ilgili konularda neler yapmanız gerekir?\n       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �              �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �              �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �              �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �              �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       �       